<%- include('../part/header',{title:"Робота за кордоном | Вакансії"})-%>
<!--  -->
<%-include('../part/menu/menu', {auth})-%>

<div class="vacancies-wrapper">
  <div class="vacancies-ctg-wrapper">
    <ul class="vacancies-ctg">
      <li><a href="<%=process.env.DOMAIN%>/vacancies">Всі вакансії</a></li>
      <li><a href="<%=process.env.DOMAIN%>/vacancies/type/czech">Чехія</a></li>
      <li>
        <a href="<%=process.env.DOMAIN%>/vacancies/type/polska">Польща</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <section id="vacancies">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <% vacancies.forEach(v => {%>
      <div class="vacancy">
        <div class="photo">
          <a href="<%=process.env.DOMAIN%>/vacancies/<%=v.link%>">
            <img src="<%=v.faceImage%>" alt="avatar" />
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="title">
            <a href="<%=process.env.DOMAIN%>/vacancies/<%=v.link%>"
              ><h2><%=v.title%></h2></a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="info">
            <%- include("../part/terms.ejs", {vacancy: v}) -%>
            <div class="photo mobile">
              <a href="<%=process.env.DOMAIN%>/vacancies/<%=v.link%>"
                ><img src="<%=v.faceImage%>" alt="avatar"
              /></a>
            </div>
            <div class="payment">
              <div class="payment-mounth">
                <%= v.paymentMounth %>
              </div>
              <div class="payment-hour">
                <%= v.payment %>
              </div>
              <a href="<%=process.env.DOMAIN%>/vacancies/<%=v.link%>"
                ><div class="button">Переглянути</div></a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- content end -->
      </div>
      <%}) %>
    </div>
    <div class="profiles">
      <%- include('../part/profiles') -%>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="profiles-link">
    <a href="#profiles">Замовити</a>
  </div>
</div>
<%- include('../part/footer')-%>
<script src="/javascripts/vacancies.script.js"></script>
